''''"Private Hutt"''' was a derogatory term that [[drill instructor]] [[Sergeant/Legends|Sergeant]] [[Jankar]] used for [[Imperial Army/Legends|Imperial Army]] recruits who did not perform satisfactorily during conditioning exercises. With the nickname came an hour of running laps every night.

